Kōrero: Te tāpoi Māori – Māori tourism Early tourism in New Zealand was based around Rotorua’s geothermal features, where Māori ran the tourist industry, and Māori women guides became household names. Gopala takenga o te ingoa tuatahi. Means "cow protector" from Sanskrit गो (go) meaning "cow" and पाल (pala) meaning "guard, protector" Haere Gopala takenga o te ingoa tuatahi. Ingoa whakamutunga Krishnan tino noa i roto i Kuwait, Malaysia, Oman, Singapore, United Arab Emirates. Haere Krishnan ingoa horahanga. Ingoa faaauhia hoki Gopala i roto i whenua rerekē me ngā reo: Gopal. Haere Gopala i ētahi atu reo. Ingoa whānau te nuinga noa ki te ingoa Gopala: Krishnan. Haere Rārangi o ngā ingoa whānau ki te ingoa Gopala. Te nuinga ingoa noa ki te ingoa whakamutunga Krishnan: Aadithya, Hari, Sandhyaa, Krishnan, Diwakar. Haere Ingoa e haere ki Krishnan. Hototahi o Gopala a Krishnan he 85%. Haere Hototahi o Gopala a Krishnan.

Hōria Ko Hōria (საქართველო, Sakartvelo) he whenua ki Ūropi. Ko ngā whenua e tūtata ana ko Rūhia, ko Whenua Korukoru, ko Āmenia, ko Atepaihānia. Tāone nui[edit | edit source] Ko Tbilisi te tāone matua o te whenua nei. Ētahi atu o ngā tāone o taua whenua ko Kutaisi, ko Batumi, ko Rustavi, ko Zugdidi, ko Gori, ko Poti, ko Akhaltsikhe, ko Sukhumi, ko Samtredia. Kāwanatanga[edit | edit source] Ko Mikheil Saakashvili te tumuaki o Hōria, ko Nikoloz Gilauri te pirimia. Hoto ki waho[edit | edit source] - Kāwanatanga o Hōria (reo Pākehā)

Arihant tikanga ingoa pai: Ratarata, Hūkokikoki, Hou, Waimarie, Kaha. Haere Arihant tikanga o te ingoa. Singh pai tikanga ingoa: Kaha, Hūkokikoki, Ahua, Ratarata, Tahuri. Haere Singh tikanga o ingoa. Singh takenga. From Sanskrit सिंह (sinha) meaning "lion". In 1699 Guru Gobind Singh gave all his Sikh male followers the surname Singh and all females Kaur. Haere Singh takenga. Ingoa whakamutunga Singh tino noa i roto i Canada, India, Malaysia, Awherika ki te tonga, United Basileia. Haere Singh ingoa horahanga. Ingoa whānau te nuinga noa ki te ingoa Arihant: Jain, Sandheliya, Seth, Bandi, Bakliwal. Haere Rārangi o ngā ingoa whānau ki te ingoa Arihant. Te nuinga ingoa noa ki te ingoa whakamutunga Singh: Sandeep, Navneet, Deepak, Aditya, Smriti. Haere Ingoa e haere ki Singh. Hototahi o Arihant a Singh he 73%. Haere Hototahi o Arihant a Singh.

Āmenia Ko Āmenia (Հայաստան, Hayastan) he whenua ki Ūropi. Ko ngā whenua e tūtata ana ko Whenua Korukoru, ko Hōria, ko Nagorno-Karabakh, ko Atepaihānia, ko Īrāna. Tāone nui[edit | edit source] Ko Yerevan te tāone matua o te whenua nei. Ētahi atu o ngā tāone o taua whenua ko Gyumri, ko Vanadzor, ko Ejmiatsin, ko Hrazdan, ko Abovyan, ko Kapan, ko Armavir, ko Gavar, ko Artashat. Kōrero: Matariki – Māori New Year Once a year, twinkling in the winter sky just before dawn, Matariki (the Pleiades) signals the Māori New Year. Traditionally, it was a time for remembering the dead, and celebrating new life. In the 21st century, observing Matariki has become popular again. Heaven-bound kites, hot-air balloons and fireworks help mark the occasion. Nīkau Ko te Nīkau he rākau whakauru, he rākau taketake o Aotearoa. Ka whakamahia ngā rau hei rauwhare. Ki ētahi, he ingoa reo Māori anō mō te mea pakeke rawa, arā he Kaihuia. Ka kohia te rito o te nīkau, hei kai. Kei ngā moutere mahana o te Moana-nui-a-Kiwa, ko nīkau he ingoa mō ngā rau o te niu, arā o te kokonati. Ko te ingoa pūtaiao he Rhopalostylis sapida, ko te ingoa reo Pākehā he Nīkau palm. Ahakoa ko te Kirihimete te wā ka tino whai rawa ngā wāhi tiaki niho, i te hiahia tonu a Takuta Waghorn ki te whakahoki i te aroha ki ngōna turoro maha e kaha nei te tautoko i ai a, nana i tono atu ki ngōna hoa mahi mō te tautoko i tēnei koha. Koinei te tau tuatoru kua whēnei a Takuta Waghorn, i te tau tuatahi 350 ngā turoro i tae mai, mai i Kataia tae atu ki Kirikiriroa, i tēnei tau, kua aro kia Tāmaki i te uru. I tēnei tau i whakarite e Takuta Waghorn i te kaupapa 'Smile Plan', Korekau he moni hua, whitu tara ia wiki te utu mō te tiaki ngā niho katoa, ko te kirimana mō tenei, ko te pono me te tika.

You are here: Whakakape Kua hangaia te paetukutuku nei i ngā mōhiohio kua haramai i ngā mātāpuna o roto i Te Tāhuhu o te Mātauranga (Aotearoa), ā, ka whakarerekētia pea i runga i te kore pānui atu. I roto i āna mahi, kua kaha Te Tāhuhu kia tika tonu ngā mōhiohio, ā, kia hou tonu hoki i te wā ka whakaputaina. Heoi anō, ehara nōna te haepapa mēnā kei roto he hapa, he whakarerenga, he takarepa rānei. Ahakoa he aha te whakarite a te ture, te wairua tōkeke whakakāhore rānei, kāore e herea Te Tāhuhu o te Mātauranga (Aotearoa), me ōna kaimahi, ōna māngai, ōna mātanga ki tētahi ngaromanga, raruraru rānei ka puta mai pea (tae noa ki te ngaromanga me te raruraru hāngai kore, motuhake, heipū noa rānei) i te whakamahi, te whakapono rānei i ngā mōhiohio, ahakoa ko tētahi mahi whakahoehoe, tētahi whakarerenga rānei te pūtake, kāore rānei.
